    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine is strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, ensuring a dependable driving experience for its next owner. While the exterior shows some minor signs of normal use, the interior is clean and free of major wear. It\u2019s a reliable car that is ready for the road with no immediate repairs needed.",
