    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is recommended primarily for those seeking a comprehensive restoration project or a reliable source of spare parts. The exterior exhibits significant wear, including heavy rust along the wheel arches and lower door panels, and the paint has faded considerably over time. Mechanically, the car requires substantial work, as the engine runs roughly and the transmission shows signs of slipping. Inside, the upholstery is torn in several places and the dashboard has developed multiple cracks from sun exposure. While it is currently not roadworthy, it remains a complete unit for someone with the tools and time to bring it back to life.",
      "price": 4000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
